{
  "stem": "23641.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we came there, and we were waiting till they-- somebody come and take us to Sobibor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, Falkenburg arrived there, and when he saw me, he took me out from there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, you come out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're going to work for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that's what I did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I, I went out, and I started to work with Falkenburg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Meanwhile, we didn't know what was going on in Sobibor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the other people went back to Sobi-- went to Sobibor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we didn't know what was going on there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But after, after a while-- after a few months later, somebody run away-- a few people run away from there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They came back to the city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they told us what Sobibor is all about.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's why we knew what Sobibor is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And those people, what they went to Sobibor after Falkenburg took me out, they never came back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, my two brother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took him away from the village as a shepherd in 1942.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took him out-- took him away, and they destroyed him in Sobibor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister went the same time with me, as, as they took away all the workers from Falkenburg.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they, they took us to the railroad station, 194-- 1942.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somehow Falkenburg came to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He took out 500 people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was one of the 500 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my sister, at that time, she went to Sobibor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And never saw her since then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She said that I should see to it that Falkenburg should take me out because, she said, at least let one survivor-- let you-- you should-- you be one survivor from our family.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was-- that was the last word I heard from her.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
